            "value": "<p>One of your ancestors was a mortal who mastered magic.</p>\n<p><strong>Tradition</strong> arcane</p>\n<p><strong>Bloodline Skills</strong> Arcana, Society</p>\n<p><strong>Sorcerous Gifts</strong> cantrip @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Detect Magic], 1st: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Force Barrage], 2nd: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Dispel Magic], 3rd: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Haste], 4th: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Translocate], 5th: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Scouting Eye], 6th: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Disintegrate], 7th: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Retrocognition], 8th: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Quandary], 9th: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Implosion]</p>\n<p><strong>Bloodline Spells</strong> initial: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Ancestral Memories], advanced: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Extend Blood Magic], greater: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Arcane Countermeasure]</p>\n<p><strong>Blood Magicâ€”Imperious Defense</strong> Raw magic emanates from every cell in your body, protecting you. Until the start of your next turn, you gain your choice of either a +1 status bonus to AC or a +1 status bonus to saving throws.</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feat-effects.Item.Effect: Imperial Blood Magic]</p>"
